herdstat - a utility that parses Gentoo's herds.xml and displays
developer/package statistics.

http://developer.berlios.de/projects/herdstat/

Please submit bugs and patches via http://bugs.gentoo.org/.

Install
=======
Run:
  ./configure
  make
  make install

Usage
=====
Read herdstat(1) for information on using herdstat.
Running herdstat --help will also display detailed usage
information.
